            <title>[PIG-4212] Allow LIMIT of 0 for variableLimit (constant 0 is already allowed)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4212</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Somehow &lt;br/&gt;
    limit A 0 &lt;br/&gt;
is currently allowed but not&lt;br/&gt;
   limit A B.count - B.count &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;d like the latter to be also allowed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
